00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:37.220
is the smartphone.

00:00:37.220 --> 00:00:39.670
But what we're seeing
is a whole ecosystem

00:00:39.670 --> 00:00:47.270
of smart and connected
devices coming to the fore,

00:00:47.270 --> 00:00:51.500
and coming to the fore like
smart TVs, smart watches,

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:52.680
smart cars.

