We've seen this slide before
just from Mateo's presentation.

00:01:19.390 --> 00:01:23.940
But I think what it does, it
captures the point really well.

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:27.970
For you as developers,
it's a key challenge

00:01:27.970 --> 00:01:31.920
to find strategies that take
advantage of the growing

00:01:31.920 --> 00:01:33.310
connected device ecosystem.

00:01:36.730 --> 00:01:40.690
And what we've seen
across categories of apps

00:01:40.690 --> 00:01:46.570
is that frequent regular
interactions with your app

00:01:46.570 --> 00:01:51.740
build loyal audiences
and increase

00:01:51.740 --> 00:01:55.770
your chances of building
long-term customers

00:01:55.770 --> 00:01:58.960
or long-term relationship
with your users.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.740
So what I want to
do today is look

00:02:01.740 --> 00:02:06.880
at how you can build
smart interaction

00:02:06.880 --> 00:02:10.375
strategy for the multi-device
contextual world.

00:02:14.570 --> 00:02:15.310
Oh, sorry.

00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:17.750
I'm not in the spotlight.

